             was indicted for <rs id="t17960113-91-off510" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960113-91-off510" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960113-91-off510" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960113-91-cd511" type="crimeDate">4th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960113-91-off510 t17960113-91-cd511"></join>, a silver watch, value 40s. and one metal chain, value 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17960113-91-victim967" type="victimName">
                  Juan 
                  Chevrier
               <interp inst="t17960113-91-victim967" type="surname" value="Chevrier"></interp>
