                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960113-91-off510 t17960113-91-victim967"></join>
                  </persName>
            .(The prosecutor and prisoner being foreigners, an interpreter and a Jury of half foreigners were sworn.</p>
         
               <p>JURY.</p>
